Security Supervisor ( Arabic Speaking Only )
Hotel
Location:
Shaikh Zayed Road, Dubai
Date: 06-05-2014
Payrate: 2,000 To 2,500 Monthly (AED)
Salary Details:
You will be entitled to the Monthly Service Charge
Job Type: Employee
Job Status: Full Time
Shift: Evenings
Categories:
Hospitality
